<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Eden huona ei suonteu mawl ziekin,
 Gitloh thihna'n vai a hawm ie;
 Thihna thazakna thim nuoiah,
 Mipi sang tamtak a mau ui,
 Hukdampa piek tiem chu ngakin.

[V2]
 Halleluia, Amen, Amen !
 Van hehpih pak si-al mel a lang tai;
 Ka tha nunnuom in zaila sa'n,
 A mangsa van pielgal a khun,
 Aw hun pui kit ina.

[V3]
 2. Lal lunggulh Tanpa hung pien ni ding chu,
 Abra'm, Mosie, Lal David in;
 Ngaiin gamla tak a thil ui,
 Ginnan a Hukdampau ni chu,
 A na muu a a kipak ui.

[V4]
 3. Van hehpihna pak Si-al mel hawih chu
 Zuiin ka tha lungkham lo in;
 Thihnan a tha hun zak khum in,
 Gitloh galin hun huol mah leu,
 Bittak in nang hun pui ina.

[V5]
 4. Gitloh a thiemloh chan ka lau ta puoi,
 Lal thisan lul ka gin ziek in;
 Van hehpihna tuipi kiting,
 Kalvari-a hung luong dawk khan,
 Ka kieng ka kimah ei chup hi.</lyrics>
<title>Halleluijah Amen</title>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>29</hymn_number>
</song>